      protected AbstractSearcher​(java.awt.image.BufferedImage raster, int side, double deviationThreshold)
      Constructs an AbstractSearcher that will search the given raster of elevation data for square regions of side pixels in size that contain elevation data whose standard deviation does not exceed a preset threshold value.
      protected AbstractSearcher​(java.awt.image.BufferedImage raster, int side, double deviationThreshold, int firstPosition, int endPosition)
      Constructs an AbstractSearcher that will search the given raster of elevation data for square regions of side pixels in size that contain elevation data whose standard deviation does not exceed a preset threshold value, at every position between firstPosition (inclusive) and endPosition (exclusive).

      • runSearch

        public void runSearch​(Searcher.SearchListener listener)
        Attempts all positions specified for this Searcher in turn, emitting information about any position that appears to produce a match to the provided Searcher.SearchListener object.

        The SearchListener methods are invoked on the thread that calls this method.
